body:
### Orbital Enterprises Open Source Projects

This is the GitHub page for the [Orbital Enterprises blog](http://blog.orbital.enterprises).
Our blog discusses third party gaming APIs (just EVE Online at the moment), and some of
these discussions lead to open source projects which we host on GitHub [here](https://github.com/OrbitalEnterprises).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
